parameters:
No way, buhi~ You're going to undergo my
interrogation from now on, buhi~
(I have to somehow create an opening...)

Are you sure you can handle this alone, piggy?
Shouldn't you call your friends for help?

Shut up, buhi! Are you also treating me like a
failure, buhi!?

This time, I'll succeed on my own and earn
everyone's recognition, buhi!
Buhahi! Don't make fun of me, buhi!

The head-opening device, buhi, brings back
memories, buhi~ With this, my head was also
thoroughly mixed up, buhi~
Hmph! As expected, the cyborg is hard, buhi!
Ah! S-Stop... Stop it... Stop it!

Ohoho, I got it, buhi! Such a beautiful brain,
buhi~

If I remember correctly, they poked around here
when it was my turn.
Oh, did I make a mistake, buhi? Then, over here.

Huh? Something seems off, buhi. Well, never mind.
Let's have you introduce yourself right away,
buhi!
A-Ah... M-My, my name is...! E-Esuka...

When the enhanced imperial soldier fiddles with
the needle he stuck in, her mouth moves
reflexively.

Buhihihi! What a cute name, buhi! Since we're
here, let's try various things, buhi!

Buhihi!? What's with this one, suddenly wetting
herself...

Haa~n, so this is the pee switch, buhi?
Interesting, buhi~
Ahhhh! I, I'm cumming, it, it won't stop!

Perhaps pleased with Esuka's reaction, the
Strengthened Imperial Soldier inserts the needle
over and over again.
Now, can you talk normally, buhi?
Hyu... Hyu... I, I'll kill, I'll kill you...!
Buhihihi! Is it okay to say such things, buhi?

Buhihihihi! This is the best, buhi! I'll make you
my bride and play with you every night, buhi!
D-don't mess with me! You... pig...!

Even if you wet yourself and glare at me, I'm not
scared, buhi!

Who would ever become the bride of a pig like
you...!
Did you perhaps have a man you liked?
Ugh... Shut up! Stop this, please... Hmm.

What a shock, buhi... The young ones these days
are so unruly, buhi...! Tell me his name, buhi!
I'll find him and kill him, buhi!
Wh-who would...! With someone like you...!
Ooh, ohh! Shu, I like Shuu, I love Shuu!

Buhihi! What a bitch, buhi! This calls for a
punishment, buhi~!

Buhahahahaha! I'll even hear about this and that
from Esuka-chan, buhi~
